image_analysis.description: A photograph of a kitchen interior. The kitchen features cream-colored, floor-to-ceiling cabinetry with small round knobs. There is a gray countertop with a built-in black gas stovetop and oven. On the left side of the counter, there are stacked wooden and acrylic boxes. To the right, there is a white refrigerator. Two metal rolling carts with glass shelves are visible in the foreground and mid-ground. The floor is covered in a dark blue carpet.
image_analysis.layout: Interior kitchen scene showing cabinets, appliances, and mobile carts.
